[{"Code":"en","Title":"QRIS","Slug":"draft-qris","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8h-yi0s88-168\"><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8i-us886z-169\"><a id=\"_rgwl05coo69f\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8j-2n4ovk-170\"><a id=\"_9j6h54imkhti\" display=\"false\"></a></h2><h2 data-block-id=\"mmka8lz9-ai8qva-211\">Glossary</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8k-j2hbk7-171\"><strong>Terms</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8k-0muxp8-172\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-426z65-173\">PTEN</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-tml7f5-174\">lembaga vital dalam ekosistem pembayaran digital Indonesia yang mengurus rekonsiliasi, kliring, dan manajemen data QRIS</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-bnrumc-175\"><a id=\"_hbvftyg2k24s\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-vc4swd-176\"><a id=\"_v6x3g0ggqdjb\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-t0kb0l-177\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-gfmzpw-178\"><strong>Can Apply for Alfamart</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-q614lw-179\">Indonesian Entity (PT/CV/Yayasan)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-5mz6df-180\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-ynisue-181\">Indonesian Entity (Perseroan perorangan/PP)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8l-sch5wl-182\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-9kz365-183\">Indonesian Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-iud1gs-184\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-cpe5az-185\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-8ltri8-186\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-ggxfhi-187\"><a id=\"_e3fvq37sde40\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-72f3hv-188\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbpgxvk-keu4uy-354\">Below are the requirements from merchant:</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8m-njx35t-190\"><a id=\"_5e8xeez71ppg\" display=\"false\"></a></h2><ul data-block-id=\"mmbpee8n-f4ti0y-191\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8n-me7kfl-192\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cq-obgk9n-189\">Business name (not more than 25 characters included space)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8n-me7kfl-192\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbphlo0-uf394u-357\">Legal name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-yo2jvz-193\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cq-3dikq9-190\">Detail of City &amp; Post code</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-jucx5m-194\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cq-7xp7ha-191\">NPWP number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-dx8z3m-195\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cq-7vc0rx-192\">KTP / KITAS number</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-ejrthz-196\"><strong>Note:</strong><br type=\"inline\">If merchant is individual, no need to provide NPWP number </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-ejrthz-196\">If merchant’s director is foreign, please provide KITAS number </p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-iwvxkb-199\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-l4uzgi-200\">QRIS  activated in 3 - 5 <span contenteditable=\"false\" translate=\"no\" data-glossary=\"working days\" data-glossary-name=\"working days\" id=\"blockglossary\" class=\"fr-deletable popover__title\">{{glossary.working days}}</span> from the date merchant submits complete requirements to MO</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-3p05u3-201\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-6vrgaf-202\"><a id=\"_i6yyhbhwx1h\" display=\"false\"></a>Via Dashboard</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8o-hql6c3-203\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-jd4rrr-204\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-vxk7hz-205\"><strong>Owner</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-9bzj4m-206\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-hfiyjm-207\">Merchant submits request by clicking activate button on add payment methods tab on  merchant dashboard </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-g36254-208\">Merchant Dashboard</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-oj0cy9-209\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-hp7evg-210\">Merchant’s request will listed in QRIS dashboard </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8p-yffo3i-211\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-recj4a-212\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-yxxyufre.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cs-w6pn3t-193\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-4z6iy9-213\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-pfjykv-214\">Since QRIS proceed through API, those request will proceed direct to PTEN, and will automatically activated once PTEN provide NMID for QRIS activation</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-i7f4l0-215\">Automatic submission will run 2x per day, typically at ~11AM and 3PM (daily)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-du6h38-216\">API - Dashboard</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-jpaybp-217\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8q-x5yxb3-218\">Please see the status in the QRIS - Dashboard. If status:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-430skq-219\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-naxkkx-220\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cs-gj2kot-194\">Approved: merchants’ QRIS should’ve been activated</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-w6q1f8-221\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cs-a7jk54-195\">Awaiting_partner_action: still in the process by PTEN</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-x5yro8-222\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cs-mjhq7z-196\">Awaiting_merchant_data: additional information required</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-16wxxf-223\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cs-s5hvda-197\">Rejected: can raise to #mo-request or <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aaPKCe_IJRjmSNuFaARA70Jng0I9TlX79aeb3SKOQAw/edit?gid=1641107815#gid=1641107815\"><u>[ID] CS OS &lt;&gt; MO Tracker (CA only)</u></a> to check / clarify with MO</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-cv717s-224\">Please see this Troubleshoot section where there are anomalies (e.g: passed SLA but still awaiting partner, status approved but not yet active on merchant dashboard etc)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cs-g6gqyk-198\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-49uctn-225\"><a id=\"_l3ikm1alkxg6\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-9s169s-226\"><a id=\"_z1yvq9q5nywe\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h3 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-bq8zkw-227\"><a id=\"_zet70wax23c6\" display=\"false\"></a></h3><h3 data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-s6ge08-228\"><a id=\"_t7df9stpmjss\" display=\"false\"></a>Manual Submission</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:60px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-y1jvxd-229\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-poqnfi-230\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-o3v6m9-231\"><strong>Owner</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-xdgl7y-232\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-hg6kl8-233\">For cases where manual submission are required, eg:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-hae5z9-234\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-zg8gb1-235\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64ct-xz4rlo-199\">Migration from Dana QRIS to Xendit QR (merchant cannot resubmit thru their own dashboard)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-37q0n7-236\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64ct-6u4l05-200\">Any error causing automatic submission via AD not working</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8r-c07y4t-237\">MO will submit applications manually. For Sales / CS to please raise to #mo-request or <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aaPKCe_IJRjmSNuFaARA70Jng0I9TlX79aeb3SKOQAw/edit?gid=1641107815#gid=1641107815\"><u>[ID] CS OS &lt;&gt; MO Tracker (CA only)</u></a> </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-v76rx5-238\">Sales / CS</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-t0wnfa-239\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-w11s15-240\">Once applications request are received, MO will generate merchant’s data through <a href=\"https://xendit-prod.cloud.databricks.com/editor/queries/2560755193432761?o=3626732626433765\"><u>Databrick</u></a>, and fill in the BID in databrick to get data</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-mehpju-241\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-xak5rq-242\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-utly4v9a.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-4w0w1x-243\">Once Databrick provide data, MO will generate data / info from databrick and copy to Submission sheet</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-bu125u-244\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-2ksz12-245\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-3zd8gsac.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-jnmsj5-246\">This data is not yet completed with MPAN &amp; MID, thus MO need to generate MPAN &amp; MID for merchant through retool <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/fdb361e8-8fa6-11ef-838e-77c28764c649/Channel%20Approval/QRIS%20Acquiring%20Manual%20Onboarding\"><u>QRIS Acquiring Manual Onboarding</u></a> by submitting submission sheet through retool</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-kvds4h-201\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-dcjxf9-247\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-3x1m28-248\">MO will use this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1xMQuHVC6lMwhxwYYqSdQ6H1b4k2GP9muGvfDUPaMG1c/edit?gid=42786669#gid=42786669\"><u>submission sheet</u></a> to get  MPAN &amp; MID, attached is how MO fill in the submission sheet</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-jk3sig-249\">MO need to check : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-jrs6ot-250\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-xswj65-251\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-2i0bef-202\">Merchant name in column B not more than 50 character</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-6lpa2l-252\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-7x7ex5-203\">Merchant name in column C not more than 25 character </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-4gjisl-253\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-dakz03-204\">NPWP number is 16 digit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-wz1hxq-254\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-tesnc6-205\">KTP number is 16 digit </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-mhnenk-255\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-xfua7j-206\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Y4YDMITDGCk-eWC9m8Dlcb1RH6eIWVsi/edit?gid=1154531603#gid=1154531603\"><u>MCC </u></a>matched with merchant’s industry</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-hxhx6n-256\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8s-jplzbn-257\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-gb65b1qc.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cu-k0da3b-207\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-qlva7f-258\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-n1se0k-259\">MO will generate submission file from xlsx to csv</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-em0ezg-260\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-k7otxr-261\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-23wta10p.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-msp1jd-262\">Once completed, MO will upload to retool to get MPAN &amp; MID </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-xlumug-263\">Attached is CSV file that need to uploaded to retool </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-tydcks-264\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-6z6dm1-265\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-2wotdx9e.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-8z84n2-266\">MO will upload file csv to QRIS  retool (make sure MO choose tab <em>Prepare for PTEN upload</em>) upload the file &amp; click Generate MID &amp; MPAN</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-707z91-267\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-nxt1o6-268\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-lpldigpp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-1c14cz-269\">If MPAN &amp; MID completely generated, MO will download file completed with MPAN &amp; MID as attached </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-fjxi2s-270\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-3cpaox-271\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-wh1b7byb.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-3b4iu9-272\">The file we generated from retool in CVS </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-mlixa2-273\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-nhmdhx-274\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-iu8i8inb.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-ivqm3e-275\"> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-wc6rj3-276\">MO will copy &amp; paste these MPAN &amp; MID to previous excel file </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-gfanyc-277\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-2dcwgw-278\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-9p5se5fz.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-nxwxsr-279\">File before without MPAN &amp; MID</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-qt2315-280\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-944ub4-281\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-vovjo8t5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-y66daq-282\">File completed with MPAN &amp; MID </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-jmm2c5-283\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-shpivi-284\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-02tkqk4t.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-zecyjg-285\">MO will download this file in excel </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-84jwmz-286\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-6ot4do-287\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-ml38gwdo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-39qirs-288\"><strong>Please notes: </strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-e9arsz-289\">Before we submit this file to PTEN make sure the column P (BID) is removed, so MO only submit file with detail until column O</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-wdnxpc-290\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-y75vpq-291\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-rnn7ni2t.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-ltyuzm-292\">Attached is file ready to submit to PTEN through Filezilla</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-1seyw4-293\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8t-7qbxp2-294\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-pwlldfsi.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cw-ngk9u9-208\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-2bhbcx-295\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-hwza0z-296\">MO will submit manually to PTEN to get MID for merchant</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-n29xso-297\">Detail login access to Filezilla: </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-z4xlrl-298\">Host: 192.168.121.100</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-99cri2-299\">User name : xendit_sinar</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-rnmvga-300\">Password : [confidential, pls ask to be shared in Keeper]</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-fbgnel-301\">Port : 22</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-fs8c4q-302\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-lygaqf-303\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-s51j5x44.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-dlglob-304\">For Submission, MO will drag / upload file in PTEN_IN folder </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-k27j0l-305\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-whj2yv-306\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-fvhu420y.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-c2k270-307\">Make sure to upload the file in folder as of today’s date 2025MMDD (or see the latest folder)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-wa2p47-308\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-86y8rc-309\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-7pv2xp57.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-gaw1hv-310\">Detail file with random number file is file from API, while for manual submission submitted by MO, will use file name exemple : </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-b99ezm-311\"><em>QRIS_NMR_93600848_2025MMDD_batch1 </em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-8d1gkb-312\"><em>QRIS_NMR_93600848_20251217_batch1 etc</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-dsqrfj-313\">Once PTEN give us feedback, they will provide feedback in folder PTEN_OUT</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-h6m9rf-314\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-d2r3gq-315\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-ru46liyr.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-vop36u-316\">MO will download the file to get MID detail for merchant</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-lkkooc-317\"><em>The feedback could received in the same day or in the next day, MO need to check file with ❔  on the folder</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-j6yqrl-318\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-x58s78-319\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-dr3d8zjk.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-vpewbi-320\">If merchant approved by PTEN, they will give detail file name : </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-i5fetq-321\"><em>NMID_(submission file name)</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-q1cmj9-322\">If merchant rejected by PTEN, they will give detail file name : </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-q8le8i-323\"><em>FAILED_(submission file name)</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-qhk7e6-324\"><strong>Notes</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8u-7mlvgl-325\"><em>If the file name is random number, please note that the submission is through API, and activation will proceed through API</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-oduvoa-326\">MO will proceed feedback file from PTEN with detail of MO file submission with specific batch (1,2,3 etc)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-yyrpa8-327\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-56hl5y-328\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-t189cvgc.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-xcllwh-329\">Click each folder as per submission date, download the file </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-kdb8jp-330\">Attached is the <strong>approved </strong>feedback from PTEN</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-qyivdc-331\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-dn5bl3-332\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-oop6vjfk.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-k8pl2b-333\">PTEN will fill in the column O with NMID detail </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-3gcazv-334\">And attached is the <strong>rejection </strong>feedback from PTEN </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-nyewef-335\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-shax5a-336\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-slpo1cn5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-7a36i6-337\">⏩For merchant with rejection feedback from PTEN, MO will re-submit to PTEN and revise specific column before submitted (refer to step number 5) since MPAN &amp; MID already in place</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-478dwg-338\">PTEN</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"60\"><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cx-s4z78k-209\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-pj6itt-339\">Once PTEN provide NMID for approved merchant, MO will proceed for QRIS activation through <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/fdb361e8-8fa6-11ef-838e-77c28764c649/Channel%20Approval/QRIS%20Acquiring%20Manual%20Onboarding\"><u>retool </u></a> make sure MO choose tab <em>Process NMID from PTEN</em> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-jl7vjy-340\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-gc3awf-341\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-12y4si1y.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-etcjpk-342\">MO need to generate approved excel file to CSV file, before submitting to retool, upload / drag the file &amp; click Submit NMID</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-6zhs2i-343\"> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-rxtb8c-344\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-jake9a-345\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-7dszidpw.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-iove3s-346\">once it’s completely activated, we’ll get the confetti in the end of activation process</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-ke4ekd-347\">To make sure if merchant completely activated, MO can check to retool <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/b4787d82-1cc0-11ef-8834-d340ecb2f27d/Channel%20Approval/Payment%20Setting%20UI\"><u>channel activation </u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-feh9f9-348\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-k6p3dc-349\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-qotkwsue.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-g1v7na-350\">Merchant will get 2 lines with status ACTIVE</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-nqddeo-351\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-el03fa-352\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-qris-image-j28uo2d4.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbpee8v-iniz4u-353\">Retool</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmka64cy-50hpua-210\"></p>","SeoTitle":"QRIS","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"QRIS","Slug":"qris-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"QRIS","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"QRIS","Slug":"qris-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"QRIS","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"QRIS","Slug":"qris-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"QRIS","Description":null}]